In this directory is everything needed for a basic plot.

MyCrossSection steering file (plotting information):
  atlastest.txt

MyData steering file (data information and values):
  atlas2012_5fb_top_mtt_ljet.txt

MyGrid steering file (Information & path to grid file):
  atlastest_grid_sherpa.txt

A Grid (note the .root extension):
  atlastest_grid_sherpa.root


Try running the MyCrossSection steering file in this 
directory called 'atlastest.txt' by running the 
following in the home project directory:

  ./plot steering_docs/example/atlastest.txt